resources.string:
Hints: 
Fill in your registered email that is linked with your account
 After filling in your email, click the button below
 After clicking the button, we will send you an email containing a link for the password reset
 When you must have received the email, click on the link and it will take you to your preferred web browser
 If you did not see the email, go to your spam folder and there you will see it
 Once received, click on the link and reset your password before it expires
 In the web browser, fill in your new password and reset as intended.
Provide a valid contact email address where we can send some updates about in future.
This is your primary phone number. This is used to contact you in the future when needed.
This is your link to any destination platform, it may be Social Media Account link or website and other platforms. This is used to lead your visitors to outside the Learn Era Platform.
Your contact email will help us feed you with necessary updates and information.
Your contact number will help us get in contact with you when necessary.
Your display full name. This is publicly visible to everyone .
